ts with senior leaders who understand gender dynamics. Funding agencies can require diversity statements in grant proposals, tying research success to inclusive teams. Finally, public discourse should normalize conversations about equity; when media highlight female scientists’ achievements, it counters stereotypes and inspires the next generation.

